author: John Sharp | jsharp@al.com
title: Walmart distribution center permits OK'd, 'truly significant' project set for groundbreaking
text: A $126.9 million project west of Mobile is expected to attracted 550 jobs. The project is enhanced through multiple county, state and city incentives.
